<topic template="Default" status="Needs Review" modified="2026-04-07T14:01:06.213Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>3.2 Turning Maintenance Mode ON / OFF</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">开启/关闭维护模式</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="19. APC - Maintenance Mode ON.png" scale="60.00%" width="173" height="37" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px;">要执行 APC 维护功能，必须开启维护模式。</para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:6px; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:6px;">要打开，请按 [维护] 软键，<text style="font-weight:bold;">[维护] </text>软键的背景将突出显示为黄色。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal">要关闭，请按 [维护] 软键，<text style="font-weight:bold;">[维护] </text>软键的背景将突出显示为黑色。</li>
    </list>
  </body>
</topic>
